---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for PDF Table to Excel."
  canonicalPath="/privacy/"
>
  <article class="article">
    <p class="eyebrow">Privacy</p>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>This tool is designed to minimize stored data. Uploaded PDFs are processed temporarily for the current conversion request and are deleted after processing.</p>
    <h2>Files</h2>
    <p>We do not provide accounts, saved history, or persistent file storage. The backend writes uploads to temporary storage only while extracting tables.</p>
    <h2>Analytics</h2>
    <p>The site may use privacy-conscious analytics and product events to understand usage, conversion success, and failure rates.</p>
    <h2>Scanned PDFs</h2>
    <p>Image-based or scanned PDFs need OCR, which will be supported later. This policy will be updated before OCR processing is added.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
